{"tid":2447200,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"47歲警員跑步暈倒 送醫不治","createTime":"2021-03-15T04:57:03.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-15T05:09:58.000Z","uid":391580,"like":22,"dislike":28,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ba1f50e65be1129d428a240f6e2c6d9943b97e15","tid":2447200,"uid":391580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:57:03.000Z","msg":"高雄警界傳出憾事，六龜警分局47歲黃姓警員今天傍晚在六龜堤岸旁自主訓練，跑步時突然身體不適暈倒，身旁同事急忙進行CPR急救，並由救護車送往旗山醫院急救，可惜晚間仍宣告不治。<br />\n<br />\n47歲黃姓警員支援六龜分局偵查隊，傍晚5點左右，黃與同事前往六龜堤岸自主訓練，突然身體不適倒地，同行同事趕緊進行急救並送醫，搶救後仍回天乏術，醫院在晚間6點53分宣告急救無效。據了解，黃姓警員有心血管疾病，平日有吃藥控制。<br />\n<br />\n偵查隊長許強生說，黃姓警員是屏東人，育有兩名女兒，警專11期83年畢業， 103年到六龜服務，平日工作表現認真又優秀，擔任警職27年，近年支援偵查隊勤務，表現盡責。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RPu9r1N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRPu9r1N.jpg&h=827e5e0f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"small\"><strong>高市六龜分局偵查隊黃姓警員傍晚跑步不幸猝死。圖／取自六龜分局臉書</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">RIP🙏🙏</span>"},{"pid":"4149f554ad99b67deb332fce269855c4bb93afe1","tid":2447200,"uid":308558,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:57:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />差啲講錯野"},{"pid":"fdfb419af9e095258c53868e0bc02c8b00d24704","tid":2447200,"uid":3976,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:57:41.000Z","msg":"開心咗半秒 屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f08f213c1788f54a68fa10f725e602a428e11eb","tid":2447200,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:58:23.000Z","msg":"好彩有睇內文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4bab5f38fddc58e6bba40fe40ecb212ed524d3b","tid":2447200,"uid":305971,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-15T04:58:23.000Z","msg":"以為香港黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" cl